thread.title: Chao Du

author: Chao Du
title: Chao Du
text:
The product looks nice and strong, although the instruction is not very instructive, but still accurate, and we managed to install it ourselves.
Down side: not sending upstairs. The door was so heavy, that I have to carry it all the way to the second floor.
Another small complain is there was one small part missing in the box. They decided to send me the missing part after I sent an email to them.
